{% extends "pages/base.njk" %}

{% block title %}
    Not Found - Devel without a Cause
{% endblock %}

{% block description %}
    This is not the page you're looking for.
{% endblock %}

{% block styles %}
    ./404.css
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
    <h2>Oh noes!</h2>
    <p>
        This page doesn't exist! We looked everywhere, but couldn't find
        it.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            If you are just lost, maybe check out the
            <a href="/">home page</a>? Read some posts to pass the time
            while you find your way.
        </li>
        <li>
            If you think this page should exist, consider
            <a href="{{ repo.new_issue }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                filing an issue
            </a>
            or nagging
            <a href="{{ author.twit }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                @develwoutacause
            </a>.
        </li>
        <li>
            If you think you visited a bad link, consider notifying the
            owner so they can fix it and help others from running into
            the same issue.
        </li>
        <li>
            If you were URL-bombing, then congratulations, you missed!
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p>
        Or you can just chill here. That's cool too I guess.
    </p>
{% endblock %}
